<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Linux on Nhat Tien</title><link>https://tienldn.site/tags/linux/</link><description>Recent content in Linux on Nhat Tien</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://tienldn.site/tags/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>/dev/null trong linux</title><link>https://tienldn.site/blogs/dev-null-in-linux/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://tienldn.site/blogs/dev-null-in-linux/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="1-what-is-devnull">1. What is &lt;code>/dev/null&lt;/code>? 
 
 &lt;a href="#1-what-is-devnull" style="color: var(--table_border_color);">#&lt;/a>
 
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Trong hệ thống Linux, device được lưu trữ trong thư mục &lt;code>/dev&lt;/code>. Có hai loại file device là physical và virtual. &lt;code>/dev/null&lt;/code> là một virtual null devices &lt;strong>được dùng để loại bỏ bất kì output nào ta redirect tới nó&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-how-to-use">2. How to use 
 
 &lt;a href="#2-how-to-use" style="color: var(--table_border_color);">#&lt;/a>
 
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>output can be &lt;code>stdout&lt;/code> or &lt;code>stderr&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="21-with-stdout">2.1 With &lt;code>stdout&lt;/code> 
 
 &lt;a href="#21-with-stdout" style="color: var(--table_border_color);">#&lt;/a>
 
&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>This will discard &lt;code>echo&lt;/code> message&lt;/p>
&lt;figure class="highlight">
 &lt;div class="decoration-codeblock-wrapper">
 &lt;div class="decoration-codeblock__side">
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;div class="decoration-codeblock__right">
 &lt;button>Copy&lt;/button>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">
 &lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;Hello from JournalDev&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &amp;gt; /dev/null&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
&lt;/figure>
&lt;h3 id="22-with-stderr">2.2 With &lt;code>stderr&lt;/code> 
 
 &lt;a href="#22-with-stderr" style="color: var(--table_border_color);">#&lt;/a>
 
&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Discard error output&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Fix Microphone Noise Background on Ubuntu</title><link>https://tienldn.site/blogs/fix-microphone-noise-background-ubuntu/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://tienldn.site/blogs/fix-microphone-noise-background-ubuntu/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="solution">Solution 
 
 &lt;a href="#solution" style="color: var(--table_border_color);">#&lt;/a>
 
&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Add below script to &lt;code>/etc/pulse/default.pa&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;figure class="highlight">
 &lt;div class="decoration-codeblock-wrapper">
 &lt;div class="decoration-codeblock__side">
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;div class="decoration-codeblock__right">
 &lt;button>Copy&lt;/button>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">
 &lt;code class="language-txt" data-lang="txt">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">load-module module-echo-cancel source_name=noechosource sink_name=noechosink
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">set-default-source noechosource
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">set-default-sink noechosink&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>
 &lt;/pre>
&lt;/figure>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>the &lt;code>noechosource&lt;/code> and &lt;code>noechosink&lt;/code> are just name, you can rename it to whatever you want&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Reload pulseAudio by &lt;code>pulseaudio -k&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Choose new device in settings of pulseAudio&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
